{#
Optional quick-nav include for an extension.

What this file is for:
- Add extra links below the section entry in the daily quick-nav
- Link to subsections, tags, categories, anchors, or custom views

How it is used:
- templates/daily.md.j2 includes this file inside the nav list for the current
  section:
    {% include "extensions/" + sec.key + "/nav.md.j2" ignore missing %}
- The current section is available as `sec`.

Safe default:
- If your extension has no subsection anchors or extra navigation, delete this
  file.

Minimal example:
  {% if sec["items"] %}
  <ul>
    <li><a href="#{{ sec.key }}-top">Top items</a></li>
    <li><a href="#{{ sec.key }}-latest">Latest items</a></li>
  </ul>
  {% endif %}
#}
